text: Claudia Blomenkamp (born 30 December 1986) is a German water polo player. She was part of the German women's national water polo team at the 2007 World Aquatics Championships, 2009 FINA Women's Water Polo World League, 2012 FINA Women's Water Polo World League, 2016 Women's European Water Polo Championship, and 2016 Olympic Qualifying tournament. == References == == Other websites == * Claudia Blomenkamp of Germany looks to pass over Jorieke Oostendorp...
